title: 1. fixed issue 7: Application not working on G1.
message:
1. fixed issue 7: Application not working on G1.
URI scheme changed from:
  content://com.googlecode.traein.stationprovider
to:
  content://com.googlecode.traein/stations
DeprecatedStationProvider added to support the old URI scheme for users
who have created shortcuts.

2. added a Tips dialog.
The tips dialog is used to inform users of features.

3. added an error icon to the error dialogs of ViewStationActivity.
They are prettier now ;)
